# Normalize line endings to LF in the repository (this is a ROS 2 / Linux
# project; CRLF can break shell scripts and produces noisy diffs on Windows).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat known binary assets as binary (no EOL conversion, no diff).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.docx binary
*.db3 binary
*.mcap binary
